<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><title>Employment Agreement</title></head>
<body>
  <h1 style="text-align: center;">Employment Agreement</h1>

  <p>This Employment Agreement is made on <strong>{{date}}</strong> between <strong>{{employer}}</strong>, with its office at <strong>{{employerAddress}}</strong> (“Employer”), and <strong>{{employee}}</strong>, residing at <strong>{{employeeAddress}}</strong> (“Employee”).</p>

  <h3>1. Position</h3>
  <p>The Employee agrees to serve the Employer as a <strong>{{position}}</strong> at the location of <strong>{{workLocation}}</strong>.</p>

  <h3>2. Compensation</h3>
  <p>The Employee shall be paid a monthly salary of ₹<strong>{{salary}}</strong>, subject to applicable taxes and deductions.</p>

  <h3>3. Term</h3>
  <p>This Agreement is effective from <strong>{{startDate}}</strong> and will continue until terminated by either party with notice.</p>

  <h3>4. Duties and Responsibilities</h3>
  <p>The Employee agrees to perform duties as assigned and abide by company policies and code of conduct.</p>

  <h3>5. Confidentiality</h3>
  <p>The Employee agrees not to disclose any confidential information obtained during employment.</p>

  <h3>6. Governing Law</h3>
  <p>This Agreement shall be governed by the laws of <strong>{{governingLaw}}</strong>.</p>

  <br />
  <p>IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the parties have signed this Agreement on the date first above written.</p>

  <br /><br />
  <p><strong>Employer:</strong> {{employer}}</p>
  <p><strong>Employee:</strong> {{employee}}</p>
</body>
</html>
